      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation cases share geometry, flow regime, and hematological fluid properties representative of the intended device operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic pump at a single operating point; the intended device geometry and full operating range differ materially, reducing relevance."
