      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification that the selected turbulence and hemolysis sub-models are appropriate for the flow regime; alternative model forms considered.",
      "rationale": "Model-form uncertainty for the power-law hemolysis model and SST k-omega turbulence closure was acknowledged but not quantified."
