    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been reviewed under ASME V&V 40-2018. Seven factors were formally assessed; six remain not-assessed and are recorded as epistemic gaps. Despite achieved levels falling below required levels on all assessed factors, the package is accepted at this stage for submission tracking purposes pending remediation actions. No context of use has been specified in this minimal-profile package.",
